{"product_id":"magrada-lip-balm-marigold-10g","title":"Magrada Lip Balm Marigold 10g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe orange marigold blossoms are simply full of life! And it is not only the appearance of the sunny plant which is powerful – this summer flower known from our gardens at home also contains large amounts of bioflavonoids and antioxidants, which help to calm the rough and dry surface of the lips.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Body\"\u003eThe wonderful softening touch of the marigold makes the lips smooth and gives them a healthy, bright shine. As a bonus, the creamy composition of the lip balm has smoothing and tightening properties.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic marigold extract \u003c\/span\u003ecalms dry, sensitive, and irritated skin. As a strong antioxidant, the extract protects the surface of the lips from the negative impacts of external factors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic shea butter\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis characterised by a higher concentration of fatty acids and vitamins. The butter, which originates from Africa, is also known for its anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic castor oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ehelps to preserve the moisture level of the lips and prevents the loss of moisture through the upper layer of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic cocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e as a cold-pressed oil is a powerful source of Vitamin E.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic olive oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a perfect moisturiser for dry lips.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eThe creamy lip butter is suitable for daily use. To treat chapped lips, we recommend using a lip balm just before going to bed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eOlea Europaea Fruit Oil, Cera Alba*, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter*, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Persea Gratissima Oil, Ricinus Communis Seed Oil*, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Hippophae Rhamnoides Oil, Opuntia Ficus Indica Seed Oil*, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| EU allergen-free\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003efragrance-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e hand-made \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50234863681863,"sku":null,"price":7.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-lip-balm-marigold-10g-302690.png?v=1739897249","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/magrada-lip-balm-marigold-10g","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}